      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_1743377684598909818.png",
                "id": "talent8297",
                "key": "Scorpion Strike ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Scorpion Strike "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>.<br>Create 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bonecruncher's Energy Block</span> card and randomly place it within the top 2 cards of your deck.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/86ad2f9a487b5e1fc7f14c6d3aebf17a_4410599007213286044.png",
                "id": "talent53058",
                "key": "Stinging Spine",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Stinging Spine"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>. <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span> up to 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bonecruncher's Energy Block</span> cards from your Hand, and create 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Thunderbore Trap</span> on the opposing side of the field.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Thunderbore Trap</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After a character on this side of the field uses a Skill:</span> Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span> to their team's active character.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span>: Initial amount equal to the number of <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bonecruncher's Energy Block</span> discarded when created. (Max 3 stacks)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/aebba01f5c8d920339645f679cd512aa_3637377511333979027.png",
                "id": "talent82659",
                "key": "Thunderbore Blast",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Thunderbore Blast"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the Round ends, create 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bonecruncher's Energy Block</span> cards and randomly place them within the top 10 cards of your deck.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/2f5fbc2acab943dc5e598980c758f964_951944366199235984.png",
                "id": "talent73229",
                "key": "Immortal Remnants: Electro",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Immortal Remnants: Electro"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Event Card</span></p><p>Randomly <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span> 1 card from your Hand with the highest original Cost and create 1 Elemental Die of your active character's Element. (Only 1 such card can be played per Round)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1413702639094370292.png",
                "id": "talent36593",
                "key": "Bonecruncher's Energy Block",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/531ed6322b0a8f721e6080da7fcd72ce_4657871338015985760.png",
                "title": "Bonecruncher's Energy Block"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_6983988005936451195.png",
                "id": "talent59555",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Discard</span></strong><br>Use Action Cards or Character Skill effects to Discard Action Cards from Hand or Deck.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Energy</span></strong><br>Characters must consume Energy to use their Elemental Bursts.<br>When characters use an Elemental Skill or a Normal Attack, they will gain 1 Energy.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8995418004550741084.png",
