                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Meow...\" \"Word has it that there are big purple scorpions in the desert that chase cats from far, far away, and they never let up! As such, all desert cats have learned some tricks to avoid their gaze.\"",
